   06-14-2012 03:05 AM

   just had to say this


   i come from a small community. started playing on the varsity
   football(american) team in 7th grade(yes, i was on JV and V at the same
   time). When I started playing in college, it was strange to be asked
   "do you play offense or defense?".  Our school was so small that when I
   was in tenth grade...i never came off the field unless i was shaking
   and low. Was on every single possible team. Got to play rugby in
   college some and loved it cause it felt like highschool again.
   26/m/AL. Type 1 since 10/15/01. shots till fall05, insulin pump from
   fall 05-fall10, now on lantus/humalog
